{"tid":2151841,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★中國玩家跨區投訴台灣Game（Red Virus） 遭「遣返」回中國 Steam 其在俄羅斯區購買的遊戲全部作廢","createTime":"2020-08-11T15:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T15:22:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bc2fe2f089c8a7dccb70848d7c8856da9fd6c4e9","tid":2151841,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:10:08.000Z","msg":"台灣獨立開發者 Leonard H 製作的遊戲《赤毒》（Red Virus）以政治惡搞為主要內容，一推出即成功帶來噱頭，但也同樣引來中國玩家的檢舉。有一名中國玩家就在跨到俄羅斯區的狀態下，試圖向客服檢舉該遊戲，豈料反被「遣返」回 Steam 中國區。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n「赤毒」在各國爆發襲捲全世界為背景，講述無數中毒的 NMSLese 入侵自由世界赤化大地河流，將美國改造成 NMSLand，新鮮的題材令遊戲獲得不少用戶讚賞，但也同樣引來不少中國玩家的不滿。有一名中國玩家向 Steam 客服檢舉該遊戲，但卻因為自身跨區至俄羅斯區，故其投訴不被受理，還被引導回 Steam 中國區，以致其在俄羅斯區購買的遊戲全部作廢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/08/11/red-virus/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F08%2F11%2Fred-virus%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FlLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=b356213a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/08/11/red-virus/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"76faddd884e413fa8b4410461f157867683863a7","tid":2151841,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f45d3a9070dbbb299f206df3b15c2e058e6c22","tid":2151841,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://photocdn.sohu.com/20150304/mp4478303_1425400521273_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotocdn.sohu.com%2F2015030